Mini MTE is a little version of Plugin Markdown Text Editor Plugin (https://github.com/tovic/markdown-text-editor/blob/master/README.md).

You can write fast markdown text ( Images not wotking in preview and print mode ), The app save data automatically when you click on preview and also you can load or save in file.md.
